acceptance_criteria: "Exploration outcome is an ADR under pm-m2u1 covering: monorepo multi-tracker layout (several .agents/pm roots), cross-workspace item references/dependencies, org-level read aggregation (context/list/search across workspaces), and identity/claim semantics across workspaces; explicitly decides what is out of scope; follow-up implementation items filed only after the ADR is accepted"
